      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It functions as both a description of disinformation and a rhetorical weapon. While it is undeniably a tactic used by politicians to discredit critical reporting, the term also describes the genuine spread of intentionally fabricated content. The ambiguity allows the label to be deployed broadly, effectively delegitimizing any unfavorable news outlet or viewpoint without requiring substantive proof of falsehood. Therefore, it often serves as a broad tool for narrative control rather than just a factual descriptor.",
